        <item>
            <title>保時捷 Macan + Taycan 純電雙雄抵港　最高 784 km 續航 + 零百最快 2.4 秒</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/porsche-macan-taycan/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=porsche-macan-taycan</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/porsche-macan-taycan/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 10:30:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Porsche Macan]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Porsche Taycan]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[保時捷]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1271492</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>純電潮流席捲全城，Porsche 近日正式在香港推出純電動 SUV Macan 及新款 Taycan。適逢車系抵港，Porsche 特別於香港 ELEMENTS 圓方舉行一連四日 （10 月 24 日 – 27 日） 的「保時捷圓方車展」，現在就讓小編帶大家看看 Porsche 這兩款新車吧。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_110548-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_110548-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_110548-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Taycan（左）；Macan（右）</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kv_3newmodels-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kv_3newmodels-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kv_3newmodels-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Porsche Macan</h2><p>全新純電動 Macan 結合了優雅與運動感，配合最新推出的 Provence 車身顏色更突顯其精緻動感的美學。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271505" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-6-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-6-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-6-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲流線型 Coupé 設計</p><p>Macan 採用流線型 Coupé 設計，另外配備了保時捷主動式空氣力學套件 (PAA)，並結合擾流裝置，使車輛的風阻係數低至 0.25。搭配扁平的頭燈組件及四點式日行燈，整體車身比例鋭利且充滿張力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲四點式日行燈</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271503" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲扁平頭燈組件</p><p>車尾部分的設計更進一步體現了 Macan 的運動感。標誌性的保時捷流線型車頂線條流暢，無縫連接至車尾的平整後窗，完美呼應了無邊框車門和獨特的側裙設計，令整體外觀更加一體化且具現代感。<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112339-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112339-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112339-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>車尾的輪廓分明，尤其是「車肩」設計，強調出充滿力量感的造型。車尾燈中央嵌入如雕塑般的保時捷徽標，不僅增添現代美學，更成為了整體設計中的點睛之筆。這些細節讓 Macan 外觀既時尚前衞又不失豪華。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271504" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-5-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-5-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-5-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>純電動 Macan 搭載了容量達 100 kWh 的新一代電池，單次充電即可提供高達 784 km 的城市續航距離（WLTP ），能滿足日常通勤需求之餘，也使長距離旅程更為便捷之餘成為同級車型中出色的長途續航之選。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112322-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112322-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112322-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112410-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112410-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112410-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271502" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>性能方面，Macan 前後軸配備了先進的 PSM（Porsche Stability Management）系統，輸出功率高達 470 kW，並產生高達 1,130 Nm 的扭力，讓 Macan 能夠輕鬆駕馭各種路面條件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271501" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Macan 另外設有雙閥門技術的 PASM（Porsche Active Suspension Management） 主動式懸載調整系統，該系統能即時調節車身的懸載高度和剛性，確保轉彎和高速駕駛時穩定舒適。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271500" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>動力系統的核心為最新的 800 V 電壓高壓電池系統，這一系統作為 PPE（Premium Platform Electric） 平台的核心零件，支援高達 270 kW 的充電功率，讓 Macan 在快速充電站僅需約 21 分鐘，即可將電量從 10% 充至 80%。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112513-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112513-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112513-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Porsche Taycan</h2><p>新款 Taycan 延續了保時捷電動車的卓越設計理念，著重展現其寬闊而強勢的外觀造型，並將運動感與豪華感完美結合。車頭設計上，新款 Taycan 採用了保時捷標誌性的四點式 LED 矩陣頭燈，讓車頭視覺效果更具辨識度，同時提供清晰而精緻的照明體驗。這款頭燈設計提升了車輛的辨識度，更讓其夜間造型更為出眾。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271506" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271512" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan5-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan5-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan5-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲採用了保時捷標誌性的四點式 LED 矩陣頭燈</p><p>Taycan 的尾部設計同樣細膩，尾燈組件採用了立體玻璃質感，並在燈條內嵌入了發光的保時捷標誌。這款燈條在進入或離開車輛時會顯示帶有迎賓動畫的效果，不僅提升了車輛的科技感，也讓 Taycan 在駐車或行駛中均成為眾人目光的焦點。此外，奪目的 Turbonite 配色能更好地區分 Turbo 和 Turbo S 車型，增強了這些高性能車型的識別度及獨特魅力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271507" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112207-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112207-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112207-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271508" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲燈條在進入或離開車輛時會顯示帶有迎賓動畫的效果</p><p>動力表現方面，新款 Taycan 提供了極佳的加速和續航能力。Taycan 基本款僅需 4.8 秒，即可從靜止加速至 100 km/h，而 Turbo S 更僅需 2.4 秒，在性能上相較前代車型有顯著提升。此外，新增的 Push-to-Pass 一鍵加速功能可在短短 10 秒，內額外提供 70 kW 的動力，讓駕駛者隨時享受強勁推進的快感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271509" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在續航方面，新款 Taycan 經過改良的 800 V 直流充電系統支援高達 320 kW 的充電功率，相較前代提升了 50 kW，且充電效率大幅增強。僅需 18 分鐘，即可將電量從 10% 充至 80%，縮短充電時間提升了長途旅行的便利性，確保車主隨時保持最佳續航狀態。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271510" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271511" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新純電動 Macan 現已接受訂購*，售價：</p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 72px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Macan 4 Electric</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港幣 $1,048,000 起*</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Macan 4S Electric</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港幣 $1,198,000 起*</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Macan Turbo Electric</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港幣 $1,448,000 起*</td></tr></tbody></table><p>*製造商的建議零售價（包括首次登記税）只供參考，不包括運輸費、保險費、道路許可證、選擇性或區域性設備。</p><p>新款 Taycan 現已接受訂購*，售價：</p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 72px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Taycan</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港幣 $1,478,000 起*</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Taycan 4S</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港幣 $1,888,000 起*</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Taycan Turbo</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港幣 $3,368,000 起*</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;">Taycan Turbo GT</td><td style="width: 50%;">港幣 $3,878,000 起*</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;">Taycan Turbo GT with Weissach Package</td><td style="width: 50%;">港幣 $3,878,000 起*</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;">Taycan 4 Cross Turismo</td><td style="width: 50%;">港幣 $1,638,000 起*</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;">Taycan 4S Cross Turismo</td><td style="width: 50%;">港幣 $1,978,000 起*</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;">Taycan Turbo Cross Turismo</td><td style="width: 50%;">港幣 $2,818,000 起*</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;">Taycan Turbo S Cross Turismo</td><td style="width: 50%;">港幣 $3,388,000 起*</td></tr></tbody></table><p>*製造商的建議零售價（包括首次登記税）只供參考，不包括運輸費、保險費、道路許可證、選擇性或區域性設備。</p><p>「保時捷圓方車展」詳情：<br />
日期： 10 月 24 &#8211; 27 日<br />
時間：上午 11 時至下午 7 時<br />
地點：香港九龍 ELEMENTS 圓方 1 樓金區展覽場地</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/porsche-macanev-800v/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">全新 Porsche 電動 Macan 香港預覽   800V 架構快速充電 + 可配氣壓避震及後輪轉向</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/porsche-macan-taycan/life-tech/auto/">保時捷 Macan + Taycan 純電雙雄抵港　最高 784 km 續航 + 零百最快 2.4 秒</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
